{
  "2273850": {
    "name": "灯塔巡航 - Beacon Patrol",
    "steam_appid": 2273850,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《灯塔巡航》是一款轻松愉快的合作型板块铺设探索游戏。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >您将扮演海岸警卫队的队长，在北海沿岸航行，保护航标浮标、灯塔和水道的安全。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >与朋友合作，通过绘制最完整的地图来获取分数。同时尽享完整的桌游体验，包含《船与岸》扩展，以及数字版独占的无尽模式。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2273850/extras/102fdc32491dbcfeb9e2bac83b01cdb4.avif?t=1765963205\" width=1560 height=252 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >从海岸警卫队总部启航，拼接属于你自己的海岸地图。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每回合，你最多可以放置三张板块，与船只当前位置相连。船只会立即驶上新板块，你还可以消耗代令获得额外移动力。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2273850/extras/4705d446a70bbdd05b3885a4baa93189.poster.avif?t=1765963205\" width=616 height=400 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2273850/extras/4705d446a70bbdd05b3885a4baa93189.webm?t=1765963205\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2273850/extras/4705d446a70bbdd05b3885a4baa93189.mp4?t=1765963205\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在合作模式中与其他玩家交换板块，或在单人模式下保留板块以备下回合使用。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >当所有板块拼完时，游戏即告结束。通过探索来得分并获得新板块，让航程不断延伸至海天尽头。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2273850/extras/3839ded26db3ac895a08b9880236c300.avif?t=1765963205\" width=1560 height=252 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >《灯塔巡航》将为您提供：</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >惬意轻松的海岸探索</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >单人或与好友合作游玩</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >富有策略性的板块拼接</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >完整桌游体验，包含《船与岸》扩展</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >极高的重复可玩性——每一局都不同</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >解锁新船只、板块、海鸥伙伴等更多内容</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >支持本地和在线联机（Steam 远程同乐）</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >数字版独占内容与游戏模式</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >清新可爱的现代桌游风格 </p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >《灯塔巡航》将不包含：</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >竞争对抗的玩法</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >资源管理</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >战斗与暴力 </p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2273850/extras/8aa0e0e6ea9704b3f8ff00cbe54868a6.avif?t=1765963205\" width=1560 height=252 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>探索模式</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >通过探索获得额外板块，只要你能持续得分，冒险就会一直继续。解锁新板块和船只，开启更漫长、更刺激的旅程。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>桌游模式</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >忠实还原《灯塔巡航》桌游及《船与岸》扩展的核心体验。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>创造模式</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >使用无限板块和移动次数，按照你自己的节奏探索海岸线。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2273850/extras/da4df8808d8addb9f935f72b3a691826.avif?t=1765963205\" width=1560 height=252 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>船只</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2273850/extras/e0889a637069b8fa3f61a30181186daf.avif?t=1765963205\" width=1560 height=320 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每艘船都有独特的能力，可以帮助你在水域中前行。但请注意，它们需要娴熟的技巧来驾驭。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>板块</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2273850/extras/a9c12a5609468fa1a4c19d83b67b3a6f.avif?t=1765963205\" width=1560 height=321 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >新板块让你创造出更宏大、更丰富的地图，带来独特的组合与得分机会。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong></strong><br><br><br><strong>海鸥、地图与旗帜</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2273850/extras/78ffd1ceec99dfca11b1116fa8b10ff5.avif?t=1765963205\" width=1560 height=320 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >升起你的旗帜，选择一只可爱的海鸥伙伴，在你心仪的地图上陪伴你冒险吧！</p>",
    "supported_languages": "英语, 德语, 俄语, 土耳其语, 日语, 简体中文, 葡萄牙语 - 巴西, 法语",
